<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - RankTiers</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="navbar">
      <h1 class="logo"><a href="/">RankTiers</a></h1>
      <nav>
        <% if (user) { %>
          <a href="/account">Account</a>
          <a href="/logout" class="logout">Logout</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login">Login</a>
          <a href="/register">Register</a>
        <% } %>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="content static-page">
      <section>
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          Your privacy matters to RankTiers. This policy explains what information we collect,
          why we collect it, and how we use and protect it across our website and Discord
          integrations.
        </p>

        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>
          We collect the information you provide directly, such as registration details,
          linked game accounts, and stat submissions. We may also log technical information
          like IP addresses and device data to help secure the service.
        </p>

        <h3>How We Use Information</h3>
        <p>
          The information we collect is used to power leaderboard features, verify
          submissions, award achievements, and send optional notifications, including Discord
          updates. We do not sell your personal information.
        </p>

        <h3>Data Sharing and Storage</h3>
        <p>
          Data is stored using Supabase and is accessible only to authorized team members.
          We may share limited information with trusted third-party services strictly to
          provide RankTiers functionality.
        </p>

        <h3>Your Choices</h3>
        <p>
          You can request updates or deletion of your account information by contacting the
          RankTiers team. Disconnecting linked accounts will remove future updates from those
          services.
        </p>

        <h3>Policy Updates</h3>
        <p>
          We may revise this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted here with
          an updated effective date.
        </p>

        <p class="last-updated">Effective date: February 12, 2025</p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2025 RankTiers. All rights reserved.</p>
      <nav>
        <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">•</span>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">•</span>
        <a href="/discord" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join our Discord</a>
      </nav>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
